SC,0003
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F343A1672708429
OL,5,F"Earlier this year we announced our
OL,6,Fplans to create a digital-first BBC
OL,7,Fthat is the best live and breaking news
OL,8,Fservice in the world ` serving our
OL,9,Faudiences across web, apps, iPlayer and
OL,10,Fa new single 24-hour BBC News channel,
OL,11,Fbringing together the UK and
OL,12,Finternational channel.
OL,3,CBBC drops nightly newspaper review
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G3/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
PN,34304
SC,0004
PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F343A1672708429
OL,5,F"As part of these changes there will be
OL,6,Fsome scheduling changes and some items
OL,7,Fmay move, or be provided in different
OL,8,Fways across the BBC channels. From 3
OL,9,FJanuary The Papers will no longer run
OL,10,Fas a regular segment on BBC News, and
OL,11,Finstead we will continue to feature
OL,12,Fpaper reviews and stories throughout
OL,13,FBBC programmes including:
OL,15,
OL,16,F BBC Breakfast
OL,17,F The Today Programme
OL,18,F Politics Live
OL,19,F Sunday with Laura Kuenssberg
OL,20,F BBC News Online
OL,3,CBBC drops nightly newspaper review
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}  S      G4/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
